@jszabo98 They don't, but [the underlying cause](https://github.com/PaulHigin/PSThreadJob/blob/99bfe5adc30ed066973114ea18d7c5091197ee14/PSThreadJob/PSThreadJob.cs#L731) in PSThreadJob is almost identical:

```csharp
    ps.AddCommand("Set-Location").AddParameter("Path", _currentLocationPath).Invoke();
```

Should be using the `LiteralPath` parameter instead.

@PaulHigin should I file a separate issue [here](https://github.com/PaulHigin/PSThreadJob/issues)?
